- [x] Deleting a factor
- [x] Listing factors
- [x] Signup/login with MFA
- [x] Multiple factors
- [x] Choosing a factor at login
- [ ] Config: MFA required
- [ ] Config: TOTP enroll disabled
- [ ] Config: TOTP verify disabled

